&lt;p&gt;1. Journey&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Return&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. Destination&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. Reservation&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5. Guided tour&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct option that indicates the arrangement of the given words in a logical and meaningful order is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. Destination&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. Reservation&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Journey&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5. Guided tour&lt;/p&gt;

